(1306, 162, 'wpcf-page-capstone-1', '<h4>Each team comprises 4-6 students from at least 2 different pillars:</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Engineering System Design (ESD),</li>\r\n 	<li>Engineering Product Design (EPD),</li>\r\n 	<li>Architecture and Sustainable Design (ASD), and</li>\r\n 	<li>Information System and Technology Design (ISTD)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4>The objectives of the Entrepreneurship Capstone project are:</h4>\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li>To create a minimum viable product (MVP)</li>\r\n 	<li>To create and validate a business model</li>\r\n 	<li>To equip the students with entrepreneurial knowledge and skillset to bring a product from conceptualisation to implementation in the market</li>\r\n 	<li>Prepare the team to pitch for funding at the end of the capstone</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h4>Entrepreneurship capstone projects must fulfil both business and technical requirements. The project will be assessed by both entrepreneurship mentors and technical faculties through validation process comprising 3 days entrepreneurship Bootcamp, 3 weeks project validation and project pitching session. Successful Entrepreneurship Capstone project teams will receive the following from EC:</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>A 3:7 matching grant. (Max $7K from EC)</li>\r\n 	<li>Entrepreneurial Mentorship</li>\r\n 	<li>Upon Graduation: Eligibility for selection of SPRING ACE Grant (SGD50K) via EC</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h4>They will then commence the project work during the Capstone terms, between January to August, with a matching grant from the University. During this period,  mentoring sessions and practical workshops will be conducted to guide the students through the project and equip them with entrepreneurial skillsets.</h4>\r\n<h4>At the end of the capstone, students are encouraged to spin off their project into an actual startup. A demo day will be organised for the teams to pitch their ideas to investors to kick start their entrepreneurship journey</h4>'),
(1307, 162, 'wpcf-page-capstone-2', '<h3>Got a question?</h3>\r\nIf you are interested in the Entrepreneurship Capstone, feel free to send us an enquiry to clear any doubts you may have.\r\n\r\n[contact-form-7 id=\"147\" title=\"Enquiry Capstone\"]'),
