(1329, 11, 'wpcf-incubation-space-description', '<h2>Co-Working Spaces and Faciltiies</h2>\r\nSUTD provides a co-working open space for 10 – 15 startups, besides space startups will have access to labs and facilities available, with only a minimum fee. They will also receive additional supports such as networking, mentoring, and participation in exhibitions and conferences.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://localhost:8888/sutd/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Incubation-Space-TnC-final-12-May-16.pdf\">Incubation Space T&amp;C</a>'),
