(1359, 9, 'wpcf-education-1', '<h2>Entrepreneurship Education</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>\r\n<h3>Entrepreneurship module (UG) by Prof Luo Jianxi</h3>\r\nAs part of curriculum, students need to form a company and seek crowdfunding. EC funded students for study trip to Shenzhen to learn about agile manufacturing and the Shenzhen ecosystem.</li>\r\n 	<li>\r\n<h3>Big D Programme (PhD)</h3>\r\nThe PhD Big D Project is a self-guided project based entrepreneurial programme that transforming ideas / inventions / scientific understandings to products / systems / service. $3k initial funding from PG office with subsequent funding from EC; 3:7 matching grant. (Max $7K)</li>\r\n 	<li>\r\n<h3>IP Module in Capstone</h3>\r\nUnderstanding of the different kind of IP, how to protect, and the considerations needed for protection.</li>\r\n 	<li>\r\n<h3>IP Clinic</h3>\r\nProvide students with a good understanding on intellectual property coupled with a practical workshop on Technology Disclosure (TD) writing for patent filing</li>\r\n</ul>'),
(1360, 9, 'wpcf-education-2', '<h2>Experiential Program</h2>\r\n<h3></h3>\r\n<h3></h3>\r\n<h3></h3>'),
(1361, 9, 'wpcf-educate-experiential-1', '<h3>Start Something @ SUTD</h3>\r\nStart Something is a experiential entrepreneurship programme that aims to expose SUTD community to the startup ecosystem and educate them on to the entrepreneurial knowledge and skillset. This includes hackathons, pitching, etc.'),
(1362, 9, 'wpcf-educate-experiential-2', '<h3>$10k Challenge</h3>\r\nModelled after MIT\'s $100K entrepreneurship competition and organised by PG students with support from EC. Student teams, selected by the strength of their ideas, are matched with experienced mentors for one month to develop original and compelling business models. Winner will be awarded with a cash prize of $10,000 to move their idea forward.'),
(1363, 9, 'wpcf-educate-experiential-3', '<h3>Entrepreneurship Venture</h3>\r\nA platform for SUTD Undergraduate students to put their skills and knowledge to use, to help tackle real problems, faced by the SUTD community. We position ourselves as an innovation adaptor that believes in our students’ products and solutions.'),
(1364, 9, 'wpcf-education-3', '<h2>Entrepreneurship Capstone</h2>'),
(1365, 9, 'wpcf-educate-capstone-1', '<h4>The Entrepreneurship Capstone is a pre-accelerator programme that allows final year students to embark on an entrepreneurial project as their Capstone Project. It aims to equip students with entrepreneurial knowledge and skillset to bring a product from conceptualisation to implementation in the market. Successful Entrepreneurship Capstone project teams will receive the following from EC:</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>A 3:7 matching grant. (Max $7K from EC)</li>\r\n 	<li>Entrepreneurial Mentorship</li>\r\n 	<li>Upon Graduation: Eligibility for selection of SPRING ACE Grant (SGD50K) via EC</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h4><a href=\"http://localhost:8888/sutd/entrepreneurship-capstone/\">More about the Capstone</a></h4>'),
(1366, 9, 'wpcf-educate-capstone-2', '<h3>Got a question?</h3>\r\nIf you are interested in the Entrepreneurship Capstone, feel free to send us an enquiry to clear any doubts you may have. Contact us by sending us an email at <a href=\"mailto:contact@sutd.edu.sg\">contact@sutd.edu.sg</a> or give us a call on our hotline at +65 1234 5678. Alternatively, you can also <a href=\"http://allon-lims-imac.local:5757/sutd/contact-us/\">send us an enquiry</a>'),
(1367, 9, 'wpcf-education-4', '<h2>Overseas Entrepreneurship Exposure</h2>\r\n<h3></h3>\r\n<h3></h3>'),
(1368, 9, 'wpcf-educate-exposure-1', '<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-168\" src=\"http://localhost:8888/sutd/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/european-innovation-academy.jpg\" alt=\"european-innovation-academy\" width=\"2048\" height=\"1365\" />\r\n<h3>European Innovation Academy</h3>\r\n3-week International entrepreneurship program in France or Italy with multicultural networking opportunity and veteran entrepreneurial mentors. Opportunities for students to have startup experience in Europe.'),
(1369, 9, 'wpcf-educate-exposure-2', '<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-169\" src=\"http://localhost:8888/sutd/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/mit-entrepreneurship-bootcamp.jpg\" alt=\"mit-entrepreneurship-bootcamp\" width=\"2048\" height=\"1365\" />\r\n<h3>MIT Entrepreneurship Bootcamp</h3>\r\nThe bootcamp is a mentorship program that begins with a one-week, intensive, in-person training and culminates with a reunion at MIT. This is a highly selective program for highly motivated students.'),
